get process outcomes for artifacts

get_process_outcomes.Rd

get process outcomes for artifacts

get_process_outcomes(apathset, process, type)

Arguments

apathset

instance of artifact_paths
process

character(1) one of "buildbin", "buildsrc", "install", "checksrc"
type

character(1) one of "EllapsedTime", "Status", "PackageFileSize"

Examples

setup_demo_artifacts()
eg = select_artifacts(paste(tempdir(), "tokay2", sep="/"),
     c("IRanges", "S4V*", "a4\\."))
eg2 = select_artifacts(paste(tempdir(), "nebbiolo1", sep="/"),
     c("IRanges", "S4V*", "a4\\."))
get_process_outcomes(eg, process="buildsrc", type="Status")

#>     package version   host buildsrc_status
#> 1   IRanges  2.26.0 tokay2              OK
#> 2 S4Vectors  0.30.0 tokay2              OK
#> 3        a4  1.40.0 tokay2              OK
get_process_outcomes(eg2, "buildsrc", type="EllapsedTime")

#>     package version      host buildsrc_sec
#> 1   IRanges  2.26.0 nebbiolo1         75.7
#> 2 S4Vectors  0.30.0 nebbiolo1         55.3
#> 3        a4  1.40.0 nebbiolo1        107.1
get_process_outcomes(eg2, "checksrc", type="EllapsedTime")

#>     package version      host checksrc_sec
#> 1   IRanges  2.26.0 nebbiolo1        173.2
#> 2 S4Vectors  0.30.0 nebbiolo1         84.3
#> 3        a4  1.40.0 nebbiolo1         62.6
get_process_outcomes(eg2, "checksrc", type="Status")

#>     package version      host checksrc_status
#> 1   IRanges  2.26.0 nebbiolo1        WARNINGS
#> 2 S4Vectors  0.30.0 nebbiolo1        WARNINGS
#> 3        a4  1.40.0 nebbiolo1              OK
get_process_outcomes(eg2, "buildsrc", type="PackageFileSize")

#>     package version      host buildsrc_sz
#> 1   IRanges  2.26.0 nebbiolo1   444.1 KiB
#> 2 S4Vectors  0.30.0 nebbiolo1   650.6 KiB
#> 3        a4  1.40.0 nebbiolo1   1.113 MiB
